Comment: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為你說出自己認為是正確的事情
Comment: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也認識這種人
Comment: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要反抗整個局勢潮流
Comment: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是需要相當大的勇氣的
Comment: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這點我十分尊敬
Comment: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過也可能
Comment: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只是個笨蛋罷了
Comment: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我看這傢伙只是單純的笨蛋吧
Comment: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別把我相提並論
Comment: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們廢話聊太多了
Comment: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該走了!
Comment: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,運輸馬車將在45分鐘後從外側通過
Comment: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到達現場後
Comment: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,各自確認好自己的工作崗位
Comment: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,知道了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好啦好啦
Comment: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說你...
Comment: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是什麼啊?
Comment: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那不是我們的庫存品嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是要送往內陸的吧
Comment: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是如此
Comment: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有商會介入有點奇怪
Comment: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底在幹什麼...
Comment: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,官給品的轉賣是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂喂 任務該怎麼辦啊?
Comment: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,糟糕 他是真的很認真耶
Comment: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊 無論是吉是兇我們還有時間
Comment: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就讓我們來享受一下吧
Comment: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好啦 來去喝一杯吧
Comment: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,幹嘛啊 新兵
Comment: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有什麼事?
Comment: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,侵佔官給品...
Comment: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是犯罪行為!
Comment: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以呢?
Comment: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所謂的官給品就是由國民納稅所配給的用品所以說...
Comment: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不不...
Comment: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒想到身為新兵竟然敢恐嚇長官
Comment: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我真期待你的將來
Comment: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,拿去買個女人來爽一下啊
Comment: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等...等等!
Comment: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,侵佔官給品是...
Comment: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂...
Comment: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把他用忤逆長官、涉嫌造反來辦掉
Comment: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,開什麼玩笑
Comment: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你以為這無法無天的做法會被...
Comment: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.76,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是會被允許
Comment: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這裡的話!
Comment: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可不可以這樣收手呢?
Comment: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真的很不好意思
Comment: 0,0:09:57.85,0:10:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這白痴似乎造成了你們的困擾
Comment: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就由我在這裡來好好調教他
Comment: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是說....
Comment: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們想這樣下去引發問題?
Comment: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就這次放過你
Comment: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼 來去喝一杯吧
Comment: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯 這次幹了很多活呢
Comment: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上啊
Comment: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對於行為不正之人
Comment: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要給予相對的報應不是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要我陪你上也是可以
Comment: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡!
Comment: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我知道小姐姐妳很努力啦
Comment: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,才沒有這回事
Comment: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳的那個朋友...
Comment: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剛剛所說的那個白癡...
Comment: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有上嗎...
Comment: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,或許是吧
Comment: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我被... 妳剛剛所說的...
Comment: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,局勢潮流給沖走了...
Comment: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也變成了一個人渣了...
Comment: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰知道呢
Comment: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是
Comment: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,即便如此 這不也是普通的人嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只是想把
Comment: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那種「被局勢潮流給沖走的弱者」
Comment: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也當作是人類來看罷了
Comment: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮
Comment: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,呦!
Comment: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳已經融入憲兵團啦
Comment: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏...
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這身打扮是?
Comment: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是裝成運貨的工人
Comment: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我用雨衣把立體機動裝置藏起來
Comment: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳看
Comment: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是怎樣?
Comment: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮
Comment: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳能不能協助艾連逃走呢?
Comment: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,幫他逃走? 逃到哪?
Comment: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們想違背王政的命令
Comment: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後逃到這牆內的哪裡呢?
Comment: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只是暫時躲起來而已
Comment: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並非真要跟王政直接對抗
Comment: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然在形式上是部分調查軍團成員的反抗行為
Comment: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但可以爭取些時間
Comment: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,找齊將審議會勢力徹底推翻的事證
Comment: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我跟妳保證!
Comment: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,徹底推翻的事證?
Comment: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真的會有這麼有利的東西嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,根據呢?
Comment: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉
Comment: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這我還不能說
Comment: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那不好意思了
Comment: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我無法奉陪
Comment: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會默不吭聲的
Comment: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你就好好努力吧
Comment: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮!
Comment: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,拜託妳了!
Comment: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣下去艾連會被殺掉
Comment: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那些什麼都不懂的傢伙只會想到要保護自己
Comment: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,卻不知道這麼做會導致人類的自取滅亡!
Comment: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我知道這麼說很沒說服力
Comment: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但就算是這樣
Comment: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們也只能鋌而走險了
Comment: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當然 會盡可能不給妳帶來困擾
Comment: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 要通過席納之牆內的檢查哨
Comment: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定得借助憲兵團的力量
Comment: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們只能這樣了...
Comment: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說你
Comment: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我看起來像好人嗎?
Comment: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好人嗎...
Comment: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個...
Comment: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這種說法我不怎麼喜歡...
Comment: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為那樣感覺只是在稱呼對自己有利的人
Comment: 0,0:14:57.21,0:15:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而這世界上並沒有對任何人是都有利的人
Comment: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以若亞妮妳不肯答應的話
Comment: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼亞妮對我來說
Comment: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就成了壞人了
Comment: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好吧
Comment: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我答應你
Comment: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒想到 能這麼容易逃走...
Comment: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,噓!
Comment: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真不愧是憲兵團大人
Comment: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,平常的工作情況真是顯而易見
Comment: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你鎮靜一點
Comment: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,接下來只希望擔任替身的約翰不要露餡就好了
Comment: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個樣子我看撐不了太久
Comment: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,畢竟他跟我一點都不像啊
Comment: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,放心啦 你們的眼神都很兇狠
Comment: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且都長著一張差不多的壞人臉
Comment: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我的臉才沒長得像他那樣
Comment: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說
Comment: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果我不幫忙
Comment: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們原先打算怎麼越過那道城牆?
Comment: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,原本是打算用立體機動強行通過的
Comment: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太冒險了吧?
Comment: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且若是在還沒進入史托黑斯區之前就逃跑的話
Comment: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該就不用那麼麻煩了吧?
Comment: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼到了這裡才這麼做?
Comment: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為我覺得這個城市
Comment: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,複雜的地形可以使替身作戰的成功率上升
Comment: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且比起挑明了就是要作對
Comment: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在某種程度上表示順從來解除對方的戒心
Comment: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,反而容易爭取到逃走的時間
Comment: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊
Comment: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我明白了
Comment: 0,0:16:58.89,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊! 在那裡!
Comment: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡?
Comment: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Comment: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就從這裡通過
Comment: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以前所規劃的地下都市的廢墟還留著
Comment: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡可以通到外面的大門附近
Comment: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真的嗎? 這麼厲害
Comment: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮?
Comment: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可別說妳會害怕又黑又狹窄的地方喔?
Comment: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯...
Comment: 0,0:17:36.73,0:17:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就是很害怕
Comment: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,像你這種既勇敢...
Comment: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又趕著投胎的傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,想必無法理解一個柔弱少女的內心想法吧?
Comment: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能讓大男人在空中翻轉一圈的女孩哪裡柔弱了...
Comment: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別說傻話了 快走吧!
Comment: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不了
Comment: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不去了
Comment: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那邊很可怕...
Comment: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果不走地面的話我就無法幫忙了
Comment: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳到底在說什麼啊
Comment: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還不快點下來!
Comment: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳別鬧了!
Comment: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連! 不要叫那麼大聲
Comment: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該不要緊吧? 米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從剛剛開始啊...
Comment: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不知道為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就沒有半個人影了...
Comment: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真的是...
Comment: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,很讓人受傷
Comment: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你究竟是從什麼時候開始...
Comment: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,用那種眼神看我的呢
Comment: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏...
Comment: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮...
Comment: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會有著馬可的立體機動裝置呢?
Comment: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那些小小的傷痕跟凹陷...
Comment: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都是以前一起保養時的回憶
Comment: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我一看就知道了
Comment: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是喔...
Comment: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是...
Comment: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我撿到的...
Comment: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼...
Comment: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當時被我們活捉的兩隻巨人
Comment: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是亞妮妳殺的嗎?
Comment: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,天知道
Comment: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過既然你一個月前就這麼想了的話
Comment: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼當時沒有採取行動呢?
Comment: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我到現在還是無法相信
Comment: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,認為這其中一定有著什麼誤會才是...
Comment: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為這樣才會...
Comment: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是...
Comment: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮妳...
Comment: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那時候...
Comment: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:49.17,Default,Q,0,0,0,karaoke,不是也沒殺了我嗎?
Comment: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以才會... 導致現在這種局面不是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊...
Comment: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我內心也是這麼想的
Comment: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒想到...
Comment: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會被你逼到無路可退
Comment: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個時候...
Comment: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,究竟是... 為什麼呢?
Comment: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂! 亞妮
Comment: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳真的是個不會看時機的笨蛋
Comment: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在還有能當成是無聊的玩笑來隨便敷衍過去的可能
Comment: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總之妳快點過來!
Comment: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有些事情只要走進地下就能夠證明的
Comment: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點過來證明啊!
Comment: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不能過去你們那裡
Comment: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...
Comment: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無法成為戰士
Comment: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說啦!
Comment: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那只是個無聊的玩笑啊!
Comment: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓我們好好談談啊! 亞妮
Comment: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們還是可以好好地談...
Comment: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,夠了!
Comment: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經聽不下去了
Comment: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,白費工夫...
Comment: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要再一次把妳碎屍萬段
Comment: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女巨人!
Comment: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還好我是你心目中的好人
Comment: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你基本上算是賭贏了
Comment: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是...
Comment: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我的賭注...
Comment: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,才正要開始呢!
Comment: 0,0:21:57.07,0:21:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎!
Comment: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太遲了...
Comment: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女巨人的真面目是...
Comment: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮．雷恩哈特
Comment: 0,0:23:58.19,0:23:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是
Comment: 0,0:23:59.15,0:24:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在女巨人面前的艾連
Comment: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,卻無法變成巨人
Comment: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只因對方是亞妮 的這個理由
